      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\u2728 Here's a gem you won't want to miss! This vehicle is in true mint condition \u2014 the paint is absolutely flawless, catching the light beautifully from every angle, and the interior is pristine with no signs of wear. Everything works exactly as it should, from the smooth-running engine to all the tech and comfort features inside. If you're looking for a vehicle that feels as close to brand new as the used market gets, this is your chance \u2014 don't let it slip away!",
