    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable Daily Driver at an Honest Price! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it starts up and gets you where you need to go, making it a solid choice for everyday commuting or use as a dependable second car. You'll notice some cosmetic wear on the exterior, including minor scratches and light scuffs, and the interior shows signs of regular use. Mechanically, it runs adequately, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance down the road. If you're looking for transportation that won't break the bank and you don't mind a few imperfections, this could be a smart, budget-friendly pick!",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make a decision. The exterior shows its age \u2014 there are visible scratches, some paint fading in areas, and minor dents that are noticeable upon close inspection. The interior is functional but worn, with scuffs on the trim, some fading on the upholstery, and general signs of regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but prospective buyers should be prepared for the possibility of upcoming maintenance needs given its condition and history. This is a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who needs reliable transportation and doesn't mind cosmetic imperfections. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you can make a fully informed decision.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in good condition \u2014 a solid, well-maintained option for buyers looking for reliable transportation without paying mint-condition prices. The exterior presents well overall, with the paint retaining good gloss and color depth. You'll notice a few minor surface scratches and light wear marks consistent with normal everyday use, but nothing that detracts significantly from the car's appearance. The interior is clean and well-kept, with upholstery showing light wear on the driver's seat and some minor scuffs on interior trim pieces \u2014 all expected for a vehicle that's been regularly driven. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and dependably. The engine starts readily, idles cleanly, and performs well under normal driving conditions. All major systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, steering, and transmission \u2014 are functioning properly. Tires have good tread remaining and are evenly worn. This is a car you can drive with confidence from day one. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition \u2014 an outstanding example that is genuinely difficult to find in the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains its original deep luster, sharp panel lines, and no visible scratches, chips, or blemishes to speak of. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new with no wear on the seats, carpets, or trim surfaces \u2014 everything looks and feels as though it just left the showroom floor. Mechanically, this car is in excellent shape: all systems operate exactly as intended, with no warning lights, unusual noises, or deferred maintenance items. The tires have substantial tread remaining, all glass is clear and crack-free, and the undercarriage is clean with no signs of rust or damage. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that truly requires nothing \u2014 just get in and drive with complete confidence.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
